  line
  line `2. Subs. by Act 22 of 2019, s. 31, for "If the Director, Additional Director or Assistant Director" (w.e.f. 15-8-2019).`
  line
  line `3. Subs. by Act 22 of 2019, s. 31, for "The Director, Additional Director or Assistant Director of Serious Fraud Investigation`
