  line
  line `4. Subs. by s. 31, ibid., for "Judicial Magistrate" (w.e.f. 15-8-2019).`
  line
  line `5. Subs. by s. 31, ibid., for "Magistrate‘s Court" (w.e.f. 15-8-2019).`
